node.text:
Quesada Reserva Privada pays homage to the 5 generations of the Quesada family that led to where they are today, with bold, modern packaging that looks toward the future. Utilizing tobaccos cultivated before Manuel Sr. passed away 18 years ago, a crop that was even in height when cut which results in the nutrients being spread evenly throughout the plants, consistency is a sure bet, and flavor is top-notch. 
💨 @quesadacigars 
🥃 @wildernesstraildistillery
